data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming Gateway community, where comfort and convenience seamlessly blend in this cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bath home. As you enter, you're greeted by a spacious living room adorned with vinyl flooring that extends throughout the home, creating a warm and easy-to-maintain ambiance. The focal point of the living space is a cozy wood-burning fireplace, perfect for creating a welcoming atmosphere during chilly evenings. The kitchen, equipped with modern appliances, is both functional and stylish, making meal preparation a joy. The home's three well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for rest and relaxation, while the two full bathrooms offer convenience and comfort for the entire household. This home also boasts a practical feature--washer and dryer are included, making laundry a breeze. The roof was replaced after Hurricane Florence, ensuring your peace of mind regarding the property's structural integrity. What sets this property apart is the backyard oasis awaiting just beyond the back door. Not only do you have almost an acre of land, an above-ground pool invites you to cool off on hot summer days, surrounded by a fenced-in area that ensures both privacy and security. Beyond the fence, discover a stone fire pit, ideal for gathering with friends and family on cool evenings as well as a convenient shed that provides storage for outdoor equipment and tools. Nestled just beyond city limits, this property offers a respite from city taxes all while providing easy access to Camp Lejeune, New River, and a scenic drive to the beach.
